%%{init: {'flowchart': {'curve': 'stepAfter', 'nodeSpacing': 30, 'rankSpacing': 40}}}%%
flowchart LR
    classDef startEnd fill:#000,stroke:#000,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#FFD700,stroke:#B8860B,color:#000
    classDef activity fill:#fff,stroke:#000,color:#000

    Start((Start)):::startEnd

    Start --> UserValid[User<br/>Validation]:::activity
    UserValid --> AuthCheck{Login<br/>Failed}:::decision
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| ForgotPW[Forgot Password]:::activity
    ForgotPW --> ResetPW[Reset<br/>Password]:::activity
    ResetPW --> UserValid
    AuthCheck -->|No| Dashboard[Display Premium<br/>SOC Dashboard]:::activity
    Dashboard --> D1{Action?}:::decision

    D1 -->|Logout| Logout[Log out]:::activity
    Logout --> EndL((End)):::startEnd

    D1 -->|Incident Mgmt| IncSub{Incident<br/>action?}:::decision
    IncSub -->|Create| CreateInc[Create Incident<br/>Set Severity &<br/>Link Alerts]:::activity
    CreateInc --> MA{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    IncSub -->|Assign| AssignInc[Assign Incident<br/>to Team Member]:::activity
    AssignInc --> MA
    IncSub -->|Update Status| UpdateInc[Update Incident<br/>Status]:::activity
    UpdateInc --> MA
    IncSub -->|Add Notes| AddNotes[Add Investigation<br/>Notes]:::activity
    AddNotes --> MA

    D1 -->|ML Config| MLSub{ML<br/>action?}:::decision
    MLSub -->|Select Model| SelectML[Select ML Model<br/>RF / SVM / IF]:::activity
    SelectML --> MB{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    MLSub -->|Sensitivity| AdjustSens[Adjust Detection<br/>Sensitivity]:::activity
    AdjustSens --> MB
    MLSub -->|Thresholds| ConfigThresh[Configure Alert<br/>Thresholds]:::activity
    ConfigThresh --> MB
    MLSub -->|View Metrics| ViewMetrics[View ML Metrics<br/>Accuracy / F1]:::activity
    ViewMetrics --> MB

    D1 -->|Network| NetSub{Network<br/>action?}:::decision
    NetSub -->|Capture Status| MonCapture[Monitor Packet<br/>Ingestion Status]:::activity
    MonCapture --> MC{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    NetSub -->|Inspect Packets| InspectPkt[Inspect Live<br/>Packet Stream]:::activity
    InspectPkt --> MC
    NetSub -->|Traffic Filters| ConfigFilter[Configure Traffic<br/>Filter Rules]:::activity
    ConfigFilter --> MC
    NetSub -->|Upload Logs| UploadLogs[Upload CSV /<br/>JSON Log Files]:::activity
    UploadLogs --> MC

    D1 -->|Reports| ReportSub{Report<br/>action?}:::decision
    ReportSub -->|Generate| GenReport[Generate Security<br/>Report]:::activity
    GenReport --> MD{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    ReportSub -->|Export PDF| ExportPDF[Export Report<br/>as PDF]:::activity
    ExportPDF --> MD

    D1 -->|MITRE Heatmap| MitreMap[View MITRE<br/>ATT&CK Heatmap]:::activity
    MitreMap --> MD

    D1 -->|Custom Viz| CustomViz[Create Custom<br/>Visualisations]:::activity
    CustomViz --> MD

    D1 -->|DurianBot Enhanced| ChatBot[Use DurianBot<br/>Enhanced<br/>ATT&CK-Aware]:::activity
    ChatBot --> MD

    MA -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MB -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MC -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MD -->|Yes| Dashboard

    MA -->|No| E1((End)):::startEnd
    MB -->|No| E2((End)):::startEnd
    MC -->|No| E3((End)):::startEnd
    MD -->|No| E4((End)):::startEnd
